lines.value: কম্পিউটার বর্তমান যুগর হাবিত্ব ডাঙর আবিস্কারহান। কম্পিউটার বুলতারা যন্ত্র এগ ইলেকট্রনিক্স যন্ত্রগ যেগল আমি গাণিতিক বারো সত্য অসত্য বিচরি নিয়ামপারা ত্বরাকরে কোন ভুলভ্রান্তি নায়া করে পারিয়ার। উতাবাদে এ যন্ত্র এগ এলা সিনেমা বিভিন্ন গ্রাফচিত্র রঙ বেরঙ নানান খেল খেলা পারিয়ার। আগেকার যুগে মানু হুরু হুরু হিলনো সংখ্যা লেহানির কাম করলা। লেটিন ঠারে এর হুরু হুরু হিল উতারে কালক্স calx বুলতারা বারো হুরু হুরু হিলনো সংখ্যা লেহানি এহানরে ক্যালকুলি বুলতারা। এরে calculi ওয়াহি এগত্ত ইংরেজী calculate ওয়াহি এগ আহেসেগ বারো এরে calculate ওয়াহি এগত্ত আজিকার computer ওয়াহি এগর উৎপত্তি।
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: eভeলীও eশ ঊণ টড়োলআ্যো লe গূশটআ eল পeডআ্যো লআড়আলআড়আলআড়আ!!!!!মে হুরুকাং যন্ত্র আহান ব্যবহার করেসিলা নাঙহান এবাকাস abacus)। ১৯৪২ খ্রীস্টাব্দত ফ্রান্সর গাণিতিক ব্লেইজ প্যাসকেল গিরকে যন্ত্র আহান হঙকরেসিল হুদ্দা যোগ-বিয়োগ য়াকরানিরকা। ১৬১৪ খ্রীস্টাব্দত স্কটিশ গানিতিক জন নেপিয়ার এ লগারিদম আবিস্কার করেসিল। উতার পিসে ১৭৭৩ খ্রীস্টাব্দত গটিফ্রাইড উইদেম ভন লেবনিজ বুলিয়া জার্মান গিরক আগই যন্ত্র আগ লিংখাত করেসিল যেহানল যোগ বিয়োগ পুরণ ভাগ করানি য়াকরল। এসাদে নানান সময়ে নানান নমুনার গননাযন্ত্র তঙাল তঙালক নিকুলেসিল বারো ঔ দেহা স্যাতে ১৮২৩ খ্রীস্টাব্দত চার্লস বেবেজ বুলিয়া ইংরাজ গাণিতিক আগই নুয়া যন্ত্র আহান হঙকরেসিল যেহানরে মাতলাতা এনালাইটিক ইনজিন'(analytic engine)। এযন্ত্র এগর কাম বর্তমান কম্পিউটারর লগে নিয়াম মান্না অনায় গিরক এগরে কম্পিউটারর আবির্ষ্কতাগ বুলিয়া মাততারা। কিন্তু ১৯৪৪ খ্রীস্টাব্দত হাওয়ার্ড ইউনিভারসিটির ড

lines.value: কস্পিউটারর পয়লা জেনারেশনর অকরাগ অসিলতা মার্ক-১'র থাঙনাত্ত ইকরিয়া ১৯৪৫ খ্রীস্টাব্দ পেয়া। এতারমা আসে ibm 650 ibm704 ibm 709 mark ii mark iii ইত্যাদি । দ্বিতীয় জেনারেশনে ১৯৫৬-১৯৬৫ আয়া ট্রানসিস্টার ব্যবহার করানি ইকরলা। এতারমা আসে ibm 1400 cdc 1604 rca 501 ইত্যাদি । তৃতীয় জেনারশনর ১৯৬৬-১৯৭৫ কম্পিউটাররমা ibm 360 ge 600 pdp 8 এতার নাঙ মাতে পারিয়ার। এবাকা আমি যে কম্পিউটার ব্যবহার করিয়ার উতা চতূর্থ জেনারশনর কম্পিউটার।

lines.value: এগই কম্পিউটারর খইতুগ । পুরা নাঙহান সেন্ট্রাল প্রসেসিং ইউনিট central processing unit । সিপিইউ গর বিতরর অংশ অইলতা এ এল ইউ alu বারো কন্ট্রোল ইউনিট। এগর বিতরে সিলিকন চিপস্ল হঙকরা মাইক্রপ্রসেসর microprocessor আগ থার উগই কম্পিউটারর হাবি কারিশমা এতা দেহাদেরতা।

lines.value: কালীপ্রসাদ সিংহ গিরকে ঠার এহার বাক্যরীতি ধ্বনিতত্ব ,রূপতত্বর শব্দার্থতত্ব বারো ইতিহাসমুলক ভাষাতত্বলো মুল ফাৎকরা গবেষনা করেসে। গিরকের মতে ভাষা এহান মাগধূ প্রাকৃতত্ত আহেসেহান। যেতাউ অক আধুনিক ভারতীয় হাবি আর্য্যভাষার সাদে ঠার এহানৌ প্রাকৃতর মাধ্যমে হঙসে। লৌকিক সংস্কৃত ভাষার কথ্য ধারা উহানরে প্রাকৃত মাততারা। প্রাকৃত ভাষার শৌরসেনী মহারাষ্ট্রী মাগধী অর্ধমাগধী পৈশাচী এসাদে ডেঙা কতগ আসে। শৌরসেনীত্ত হিন্দি রাজস্থানী ইত্যাদি বারো মাগধীত্ত মৈথিলী,বাংলা অসমীয়া ঠার নিকুলেসেতা। বিষ্ণুপ্রিয়া মনিপুরী ঠারে মাগধী বারো শৌরসেনী দ্বিয়হানির প্রভাব আসে। মাগধীর প্রভাব য়াম আসেতা ঠারহানর রূপতত্ত্বত(morphology বারো শৌরসেনীর প্রভাব বপেয়া আসেতা বাক্যরীতি(syntax বারো ধ্বনিতত্ত্বত(phonology)।

lines.value: বিষ্ণুপ্রিয়া মণিপুরী ঠারর সাহিত্যর ভান্ডারে লোক সাহিত্যর সংখ্যাহান না য়্যাতসে যেতা পুরানা আমলেত্ত আজি পেয়া মানুর থতানো আজি পেয়া চলিয়া আহের। বিষ্ণুপ্রিয়া মণিপুরীর পুরানা আমলর সাহিত্য অতা লোক-য়্যারী লোক-এলা লোক-কবিতা ছড়া বারো পৌরেইত ডেঙ সালসে। অতার মা ( বরন ডাহানির এলা ১৪৫০-১৬০০ মারি বারো সরারেলর জীবনগাথাল <span class="plainlinks"> মাদই সরারেলর এলা ১৫০০-১৬০০ মারি উল্লেখ করানির সাদে। মাতানি থক এলা এতাত তিব্বত-বার্মিজ ঠার জিনার আবকচা ৱাহি তিলসে। এলা এতাই বিষ্ণুপ্রিয়া মণিপুরীর সাহিত্য বারো ঠারর ইতিহাসহান হারপানিত বারো তামকরানিত জবর পাঙকরের। অতাবুলতেউ এলা এতা গাঙ-ঘরেদে ক্ষেতি-বারির কাম করতারা বেয়াপাই য়্যাম দিতারা। বিষ্ণুপ্রিয়া মণিপুরীর পৌরেই এতাউ সাহিত্যর ডাঙর জাগা আহান কালকরিয়া থুয়াসে।

lines.value: mathematics is the discipline that deals with concepts such as quantity structure space and change
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: it evolved through the use of abstraction and logical reasoning from counting calculation measurement and the study of the shapes and motions of physical objects
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: mathematicians explore these and related concepts aiming to formulate new conjectures and establish their truth by rigorous deduction from appropriately chosen axioms and definitions
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: knowledge and use of basic mathematics is widespread as it has been throughout history
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: refinements of basic ideas are visible in ancient mathematical texts originating in ancient egypt mesopotamia and ancient india with increased rigour introduced by the ancient greeks
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: from this point on the development continued in short bursts until the renaissance period of the 16th century where mathematical innovations interacted with new scientific discoveries leading to an acceleration in understanding that continues to the present day
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: mathematics is used throughout the world in many fields including science engineering medicine and economics
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: these fields both inspire and make use of new discoveries in mathematics
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: new mathematics is also created for its own sake without any particular application in view a common practice in the branch known as pure mathematics
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the word mathematics is often abbreviated math in the us and canada and maths in britain ireland and many commonwealth countries
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the word mathematics greek uaonuatika comes from the greek uaonua mathema which means learning study science and additionally came to have the narrower and more technical meaning mathematical study even in classical times
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: its adjective is uaonuatikos mathematikos related to learning or studious which likewise further came to mean mathematical
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: in particular uaonuatikn texvn mathematikḗ tekhne in latin ars mathematica meant the mathematical art
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the apparent plural form in like the plural form les mathematiques and the less commonly used singular derivative la mathematique goes back to the latin neuter plural mathematica cicero based on the greek plural ta uaonuatika ta mathematika used by aristotle and meaning roughly all things mathematical
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: despite the form and etymology the word like the names of arts and sciences in general is used as a singular mass noun in english today
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: :main article history of mathematics the evolution of mathematics might be seen to be an ever increasing series of abstractions or alternatively an expansion of subject matter
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the first abstraction was probably that of numbers
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the realization that two apples and two oranges have something in common was a breakthrough in human thought
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: in addition to recognizing how to count physical objects prehistoric peoples also recognized how to count abstract quantities like time - days seasons years
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: arithmetic addition subtraction multiplication and division naturally followed
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: monolithic monuments testify to knowledge of geometry
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: further steps need writing or some other system for recording numbers such as tallies or the knotted strings called quipu used by the inca empire to store numerical data
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: numeral systems have been many and diverse
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: from the beginnings of recorded history the major disciplines within mathematics arose out of the need to do calculations relating to taxation and commerce to understand the relationships among numbers to measure land and to predict astronomical events
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: these needs can be roughly related to the broad subdivision of mathematics into the studies of quantity structure space and change
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: mathematics since has been much extended and there has been a fruitful interaction between mathematics and science to the benefit of both
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: mathematical discoveries have been made throughout history and continue to be made today
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: according to mikhail b sevryuk in the january 2006 issue of the bulletin of the american mathematical society the number of papers and books included in the mathematical reviews database since 1940 the first year of operation of mr is now more than 1.9 million and more than 75 thousand items are added to the database each year
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the overwhelming majority of works in this ocean contain new mathematical theorems and their proofs
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: mathematics arises wherever there are difficult problems that involve quantity structure space or change
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: at first these were found in commerce land measurement and later astronomy nowadays all sciences suggest problems studied by mathematicians and many problems arise within mathematics itself
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: newton was one of the infinitesimal calculus inventors feynman invented the feynman path integral using a combination of reasoning and physical insight and today's string theory also inspires new mathematics
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: some mathematics is only relevant in the area that inspired it and is applied to solve further problems in that area
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: but often mathematics inspired by one area proves useful in many areas and joins the general stock of mathematical concepts
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the remarkable fact that even the purest mathematics often turns out to have practical applications is what eugene wigner has called the unreasonable effectiveness of mathematics as in most areas of study the explosion of knowledge in the scientific age has led to specialization in mathematics
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: one major distinction is between pure mathematics and applied mathematics
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: within applied mathematics two major areas have split off and become disciplines in their own right statistics and computer science
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: many mathematicians talk about the elegance of mathematics its intrinsic aesthetics and inner beauty
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: simplicity and generality are valued
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: there is beauty also in a clever proof such as euclid's proof that there are infinitely many prime numbers and in a numerical method that speeds calculation such as the fast fourier transform
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: g h hardy in a mathematician's apology expressed the belief that these aesthetic considerations are in themselves sufficient to justify the study of pure mathematics
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: most of the mathematical notation we use today was not invented until the 16th century
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: before that mathematics was written out in words a painstaking process that limited mathematical discovery
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: modern notation makes mathematics much easier for the professional but beginners often find it daunting
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: it is extremely compressed a few symbols contain a great deal of information
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: like musical notation modern mathematical notation has a strict syntax and encodes information that would be difficult to write in any other way
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: mathematical language also is hard for beginners
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: words such as or or only have more precise meanings than in everyday speech
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: also confusing to beginners words such as open and field have been given specialized mathematical meanings and mathematical jargon includes technical terms such as homeomorphism and integrable
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: it was said that henri poincare was only elected to the academie francaise so that he could tell them how to define automorphe in their dictionary
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: but there is a reason for special notation and technical jargon mathematics requires more precision than everyday speech
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: mathematicians refer to this precision of language and logic as rigor
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: rigor is fundamentally a matter of mathematical proof
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: mathematicians want their theorems to follow from axioms by means of systematic reasoning
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: this is to avoid mistaken theorems based on fallible intuitions of which many instances have occurred in the history of the subject for example in mathematical analysis
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the level of rigor expected in mathematics has varied over time the greeks expected detailed arguments but at the time of isaac newton the methods employed were less rigorous
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: problems inherent in the definitions used by newton would lead to a resurgence of careful analysis and formal proof in the 19th century
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: today mathematicians continue to argue among themselves about computer assisted proofs
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: since large computations are hard to verify such proofs may not be sufficiently rigorous
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: axioms in traditional thought were self evident truths but that conception is problematic
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: at a formal level an axiom is just a string of symbols which has an intrinsic meaning only in the context of all derivable formulas of an axiomatic system
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: it was the goal of hilbert's program to put all of mathematics on a firm axiomatic basis but according to godel's incompleteness theorem every sufficiently powerful axiomatic system has undecidable formulas and so a final axiomatization of mathematics is impossible
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: nonetheless mathematics is often imagined to be as far as its formal content nothing but set theory in some axiomatization in the sense that every mathematical statement or proof could be cast into formulas within set theory
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: carl friedrich gauss referred to mathematics as the queen of the sciences
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: in the original latin regina scientiarum as well as in konigin der wissenschaften the word corresponding to science means field of knowledge
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: indeed this is also the original meaning in english and there is no doubt that mathematics is in this sense a science
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the specialization restricting the meaning to natural science is of later date
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: if one considers science to be strictly about the physical world then mathematics or at least pure mathematics is not a science
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: karl popper believed that mathematics was not experimentally falsifiable and thus not a science
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: however other thinkers notably imre lakatos have applied a version of falsificationism to mathematics itself
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: in his 2002 book a new kind of science stephen wolfram argues that computational mathematics deserves to be explored empirically as a scientific field in its own right
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: an alternative view is that certain scientific fields such as theoretical physics are mathematics with axioms that are intended to correspond to reality
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: in fact the theoretical physicist j m ziman proposed that science is public knowledge and thus includes mathematics
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: in any case mathematics shares much in common with many fields in the physical sciences notably the exploration of the logical consequences of assumptions
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: intuition and experimentation also play a role in the formulation of conjectures in both mathematics and the other sciences
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: experimental mathematics continues to grow in importance within mathematics and computation and simulation are playing an increasing role in both the sciences and mathematics weakening the objection that mathematics does not utilize the scientific method
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the opinions of mathematicians on this matter are varied
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: while some in applied mathematics feel that they are scientists those in pure mathematics often feel that they are working in an area more akin to logic and that they are hence fundamentally philosophers
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: many mathematicians feel that to call their area a science is to downplay the importance of its aesthetic side and its history in the traditional seven liberal arts others feel that to ignore its connection to the sciences is to turn a blind eye to the fact that the interface between mathematics and its applications in science and engineering has driven much development in mathematics
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: one way this difference of viewpoint plays out is in the philosophical debate as to whether mathematics is created as in art or discovered as in science
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: it is common to see universities divided into sections that include a division of science and mathematics indicating that the fields are seen as being allied but that they do not coincide
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: in practice mathematicians are typically grouped with scientists at the gross level but separated at finer levels
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: this is one of many issues considered in the philosophy of mathematics
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: mathematical awards are generally kept separate from their equivalents in science
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the most prestigious award in mathematics is the fields medal established in 1936 and now awarded every 4 years
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: it is usually considered the equivalent of science's nobel prize
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: another major international award the abel prize was introduced in 2003
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: both of these are awarded for a particular body of work either innovation in a new area of mathematics or resolution of an outstanding problem in an established field
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: a famous list of 23 such open problems called hilbert's problems was compiled in 1900 by german mathematician david hilbert
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: this list achieved great celebrity among mathematicians and at least nine of the problems have now been solved
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: a new list of seven important problems titled the millennium prize problems was published in 2000
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: solution of each of these problems carries a $1 million reward and only one the riemann hypothesis is duplicated in hilbert's problems
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: as noted above the major disciplines within mathematics first arose out of the need to do calculations in commerce to understand the relationships between numbers to measure land and to predict astronomical events
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: these four needs can be roughly related to the broad subdivision of mathematics into the study of quantity structure space and change i.e arithmetic algebra geometry and analysis
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: in addition to these main concerns there are also subdivisions dedicated to exploring links from the heart of mathematics to other fields to logic to set theory foundations to the empirical mathematics of the various sciences applied mathematics and more recently to the rigorous study of uncertainty
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the study of quantity starts with numbers first the familiar natural numbers and integers whole numbers and arithmetical operations on them which are characterized in arithmetic
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the deeper properties of integers are studied in number theory whence such popular results as fermat's last theorem
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: number theory also holds two widely considered unsolved problems the twin prime conjecture and goldbach's conjecture
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: as the number system is further developed the integers are recognised as a subset of the rational numbers fractions
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: these in turn are contained within the real numbers which are used to represent continuous quantities
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: real numbers are generalised to complex numbers
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: these are the first steps of a hierarchy of numbers that goes on to include quarternions and octonions
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: consideration of the natural numbers also leads to the transfinite numbers which formalise the concept of counting to infinite
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: another area of study is size which leads to the cardinal numbers and then to another conception of infinity the aleph numbers which allow meaningful comparison of the size of infinitely large sets
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: many mathematical objects such as sets of numbers and functions exhibit internal structure
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the structural properties of these objects are investigated in the study of groups rings fields and other abstract systems which are themselves such objects
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: this is the field of abstract algebra
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: an important concept here is that of vectors generalized to vector spaces and studied in linear algebra
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the study of vectors combines three of the fundamental areas of mathematics quantity structure and space
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: vector calculus expands the field into a fourth fundamental area that of change
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the study of space originates with geometry in particular euclidean geometry
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: trigonometry combines space and number and encompasses the well known pythagorean theorem
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the modern study of space generalizes these ideas to include higher dimensional geometry non euclidean geometries which play a central role in general relativity and topology
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: quantity and space both play a role in analytic geometry differential geometry and algebraic geometry
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: within differential geometry are the concepts of fiber bundles and calculus on manifolds
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: within algebraic geometry is the description of geometric objects as solution sets of polynomial equations combining the concepts of quantity and space and also the study of topological groups which combine structure and space
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: lie groups are used to study space structure and change
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: topology in all its many ramifications may have been the greatest growth area in 20th century mathematics and includes the long standing poincare conjecture and the controversial four color theorem whose only proof by computer has never been verified by a human
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: understanding and describing change is a common theme in the natural sciences and calculus was developed as a powerful tool to investigate it
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: functions arise here as a central concept describing a changing quantity
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the rigorous study of real numbers and real valued functions is known as real analysis with complex analysis the equivalent field for the complex numbers
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the riemann hypothesis one of the most fundamental open questions in mathematics is drawn from complex analysis
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: functional analysis focuses attention on typically infinite dimensional spaces of functions
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: one of many applications of functional analysis is quantum mechanics
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: many problems lead naturally to relationships between a quantity and its rate of change and these are studied as differential equations
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: many phenomena in nature can be described by dynamical systems chaos theory makes precise the ways in which many of these systems exhibit unpredictable yet still deterministic behavior
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: in order to clarify the foundations of mathematics the fields of mathematical logic and set theory were developed
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: mathematical logic is concerned with setting mathematics on a rigid axiomatic framework and studying the results of such a framework
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: as such it is home to godel's second incompleteness theorem perhaps the most widely celebrated result in logic which informally implies that there are always true theorems which cannot be proven
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: modern logic is divided into recursion theory model theory and proof theory and is closely linked to theoretical computer science
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: discrete mathematics is the common name for the fields of mathematics most generally useful in theoretical computer science
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: this includes computability theory computational complexity theory and information theory
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: computability theory examines the limitations of various theoretical models of the computer including the most powerful known model the turing machine
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: complexity theory is the study of tractability by computer some problems although theoretically soluble by computer are so expensive in terms of time or space that solving them is likely to remain practically unfeasible even with rapid advance of computer hardware
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: finally information theory is concerned with the amount of data that can be stored on a given medium and hence concepts such as compression and entropy
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: as a relatively new field discrete mathematics has a number of fundamental open problems
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the most famous of these is the p=np problem one of the millennium prize problems
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: it is widely believed that the answer to this problem is no
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: applied mathematics considers the use of abstract mathematical tools in solving concrete problems in natural science
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: an important field in applied mathematics is statistics which uses probability theory as a tool and allows the description analysis and prediction of phenomena where chance plays a role
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: this is used in all the sciences
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: many statisticians however do not consider themselves to be mathematicians but rather part of an allied group numerical analysis investigates computational methods for efficiently solving a broad range of mathematical problems that are typically too large for human numerical capacity it includes the study of rounding errors or other sources of error in computation
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: :mathematical physics • analytical mechanics • mathematical fluid dynamics • numerical analysis • optimization • probability • statistics • mathematical economics • financial mathematics • game theory • mathematical biology • cryptography • operations research
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: mathematics is not a closed intellectual system in which everything has already been worked out
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: there is no shortage of open problems
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: pseudomathematics is a form of mathematics like activity undertaken outside academia and occasionally by mathematicians themselves
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: it often consists of determined attacks on famous questions consisting of proof attempts made in an isolated way that is long papers not supported by previously published theory
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the relationship to generally accepted mathematics is similar to that between pseudoscience and real science
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the misconceptions involved are normally based on
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: mathematical concepts and theorems need not correspond to anything in the physical world
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: insofar as a correspondence does exist while mathematicians and physicists may select axioms and postulates that seem reasonable and intuitive it is not necessary for the basic assumptions within an axiomatic system to be true in an empirical or physical sense
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: this leads to confusion on the part of those who assume that where mathematical concepts are named after or ostensibly correspond with aspects of reality physics economics etc they have a rigorous relationship with it
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: such is simply not the case and empirical testing of mathematical predictions is not a mathematical undertaking see mathematics as science above
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: thus while most systems of axioms are derived from our perceptions and experiments they are not dependent on them
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: nevertheless mathematics remains extremely useful for solving real world problems
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: this fact led eugene wigner to write an essay the unreasonable effectiveness of mathematics in the natural sciences
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: mathematics is not about unrestricted theorem proving any more than literature is about the construction of grammatically correct sentences
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: mathematics is not accountancy
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: although arithmetic computation is crucial to accountants their main concern is to verify that computations are correct through a system of doublechecks
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: advances in abstract mathematics are mostly irrelevant to the efficiency of bookkeeping but the use of computers clearly does matter
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: mathematics is not numerology
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: numerology uses modular arithmetic to reduce names and dates down to numbers but assigns emotions or traits to these numbers intuitively or on the basis of traditions
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: সিলেট জিলা ইংরেজি:sylhet zila বাংলাদেশর সিলেট বিভাগর অধীনর জিলা আগ। আমার ঠারে জিলা এগরে সিলট বুলতারা। আবকচায় শ্রীহট্ট নাঙ এহানাত্ত সিলেট বারো কততায় সিল + হট্ট এহান তিলুইয়া সিলেট নাঙহান হঙিসে বুলতারা। সিল বুলতে আন্দি-মরকসি পিছানির হিলগ বারো হট্ট বুলতে বাজার হারপারাঙ। আগে এহাত আন্দি-মরকসি পিছানির হিলর ডাঙর বাজার আহান নাঙ কাহিসিল আরো এসারে নাঙহান অসেতা। আরাতাই বারো শ্রী মানে চুনাপা জাগাহান বুলিয়া শ্রীহট্ট নাঙহান থসি বুলিয়া মাত্তারা। সিলট এহানর মানুয়ে অতারতারা ঠার এহান বাংলা ঠারর উপঠার আহান ইলেউ নিজস্ব স্বকীয়তা আহনল চলের বারো ঠারহানরে সিলেটি ঠার বুলতারা অহাত্ব মেয়েক অতারে সিলেটি নাগরি বুলতারা।
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: অংক বা গণিত ইংরেজি ঠারলো mathematics পরিমাণহান quantity হঙপাহান structure সিলহান change বারো জাগাহান space)-লয়া গবেষণা করানি অহানরে সিদাকরিয়া গণিত বুলানি অর। আকেইগর মতহান ইলয়া চিত্র figure বারো সংখ্যার number গবেষণা অহানরে গণিত বুলানি একরের কিন্তু এহান গণিতর জবর সুজা সংজ্ঞা আহান। গণিত দর্শনর নানান দৃষ্টিভঙ্গিত্ত গণিতর নানান সংজ্ঞা দেনা য়্যাকরের। বিধিইলপা formal মিতলেঙেত্ত গণিত ইলাতাই যুক্তিবিজ্ঞান logic বারো বিশেষ প্রতীক-চিনৎহানি notation ইলকরা স্বতঃসিদ্ধ-রূপহানল সংজ্ঞায়িত বিমূর্ত হংনিহানির axiomatically defined abstract structures গবেষণা অর্থাৎ গণিত ইলতা নানান ধরনর বিমূর্ত মানসিক খেলা বারো গণিতবিদদর কাম হান ইলতাই এরে খেলার নিয়মহানিরে বারো নানান খেলার ভিতরে সম্পর্কহান নিকালানি । বারো টেইপাংপন্থী realistic দৃষ্টিকোণেত্ত গণিত ইলতাই ঔ বস্তু বা ধারণাহানরে লুইয়া গবেষণা আমার যুক্তিহঙপা reasoning হাব্বিরে যেতার ৱাইসাঙ অস্তিত্ব আসে অর্থাৎ গণিত এহান বাস্তব জিনিসর গবেষণা মানুর মনর বিমূর্ত হঙকরানিহান নাগই অহাত্ত গণিতবিদর কাম হান মূর্ত টেইপাঙেত্ত গণিতর নানান বিমূর্ত সূত্র লিংখাত করানি। বিজ্ঞানর হারি শাখাত গণিতর ব্যবহার আসে গণিতরে অহান্ন বিজ্ঞানর ঠার বিশ্বর ঠার বারো হাব্বি বিজ্ঞানর মাদৈ বুলিয়া দাহানি অর। অংকত সংখ্যা বারো আর আর মাহানি একরের রাশিহানির মা সম্পর্ক বর্ণনা করানি অর। গণিতর সার্বজনীন ঠরলো বিজ্ঞানীয়ে আগর লগে আগই ধারণা সিলকরতারা। অহানে গণিত এহান বিজ্ঞানর ঠারহান।

lines.value: the arts is a broad subdivision of culture composed of many expressive disciplines
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: in modern usage it is a term broader than art which usually means the visual arts comprising both fine art and crafts
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: a precise definition of the arts can be contentious but the following areas of activity usually are included in modern academia the arts are usually grouped with or a subset of the humanities
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: some subjects in the humanities are history linguistics literature philosophy women's studies
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: newspapers such as the new york times and the times of london typically include a section on the arts
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the great traditions in art have a foundation in the art of one of six ancient civilizations in byzantine and gothic art of the middle ages the dominance of the church insisted on the expression of biblical and not material truths
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the renaissance saw the return to valuation of the material world and this shift is reflected in art forms which show the corporeality of the human body and the three dimensional reality of landscape
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: eastern art has generally worked in a style akin to western medieval art namely a concentration on surface patterning and local colour meaning the plain colour of an object such as basic red for a red robe rather than the modulations of that colour brought about by light shade and reflection
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: a characteristic of this style is that the local colour is often defined by an outline a contemporary equivalent is the cartoon
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: this is evident in for example the art of india tibet and japan
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: religious islamic art forbids iconography and expresses religious ideas through geometry instead
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the physical and rational certainties depicted by the 19th-century enlightenment were shattered not only by new discoveries of relativity by einstein and of unseen psychology by freud but also by unprecedented technological development
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: increasing global interaction during this time saw an equivalent influence of other cultures into western art
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: drawing is a means of making an image using any of a wide variety of tools and techniques
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: it generally involves making marks on a surface by applying pressure from a tool or moving a tool across a surface
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: common tools are graphite pencils pen and ink inked brushes wax color pencils crayons charcoals pastels and markers
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: digital tools which simulate the effects of these are also used
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the main techniques used in drawing are line drawing hatching crosshatching random hatching scribbling stippling and blending
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: an artist who excels in drawing is referred to as a draftsman or draughtsman
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: architecture from latin architectura and ultimately from greek apxitektwv a master builder from apxi chief leader and tektwv builder carpenter is the art and science of designing buildings and structures
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: a wider definition would include within its scope the design of the total built environment from the macrolevel of town planning urban design and landscape architecture to the microlevel of creating furniture
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: architectural design usually must address both feasibility and cost for the builder as well as function and aesthetics for the
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: in modern usage architecture is the art and discipline of creating an actual or inferring an implied or apparent plan of any complex object or system
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the term can be used to connote the implied architecture of abstract things such as music or mathematics the apparent architecture of natural things such as geological formations or the structure of biological cells or explicitly planned architectures of human made things such as software computers enterprises and databases in addition to buildings
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: in every usage an architecture may be seen as a subjective mapping from a human perspective that of the user in the case of abstract or physical artifacts to the elements or of some kind of structure or system which preserves the relationships among the elements or components
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: planned architecture often manipulates space volume texture light shadow or abstract elements in order to achieve pleasing aesthetics
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: this distinguishes it from applied science or engineering which usually concentrate more on the functional and feasibility aspects of the design of constructions or structures
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: in the field of building architecture the skills demanded of an architect range from the more complex such as for a hospital or a stadium to the apparently simpler such as planning residential houses
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: many architectural works may be seen also as cultural and political symbols and or works of art
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the role of the architect though changing has been central to the successful and sometimes less than successful design and implementation of pleasingly built environments in which people live
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: [[image:table of architecture cyclopaedia 1728 volume 1.jpg|thumb|right|160px|table of architecture cyclopaedia 1728
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: painting taken literally is the practice of applying pigment suspended in a carrier or medium and a binding agent a glue to a surface support such as paper canvas or a wall
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: however when used in an artistic sense it means the use of this activity in combination with drawing composition and other aesthetic considerations in order to manifest the expressive and conceptual intention of the practitioner
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: painting is also used to express spiritual motifs and ideas sites of this kind of painting range from artwork depicting mythological figures on pottery to the sistine chapel to the human body itself
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: colour is the essence of painting as sound is of music
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: colour is highly subjective but has observable psychological effects although these can differ from one culture to the next
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: black is associated with mourning in the west but elsewhere white may be
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: some painters theoreticians writers and scientists including goethe kandinsky newton have written their own colour theory
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: moreover the use of language is only a generalisation for a colour equivalent
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the word red for example can cover a wide range of variations on the pure red of the spectrum
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: there is not a formalised register of different colours in the way that there is agreement on different notes in music such as c or c# in music although the pantone system is widely used in the printing and design industry for this purpose
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: modern artists have extended the practice of painting considerably to include for example collage
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: this began with cubism and is not painting in strict sense
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: some modern painters incorporate different materials such as sand cement straw or wood for their texture
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: examples of this are the works of jean dubuffet or anselm kiefer
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: modern and contemporary art has moved away from the historic value of craft in favour of concept this has led some to say that painting as a serious art form is dead although this has not deterred the majority of artists from continuing to practise it either as whole or part of their work
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: literature is literally acquaintance with letters as in the first sense given in the oxford english dictionary from the latin littera meaning an individual written character letter
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the term has generally come to identify a collection of texts which in western culture are mainly prose both fiction and non fiction drama and poetry
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: in much if not all of the world texts can be oral as well and include such genres as epic legend myth ballad other forms of oral poetry and the folktale
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: the performing arts differ from the plastic arts insofar as the former uses the artist's own body face presence as a medium and the latter uses materials such as clay metal or paint which can be molded or transformed to create some art object
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: performing arts include acrobatics busking comedy dance magic music opera film juggling marching arts such as brass bands and theatre
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: artists who participate in these arts in front of an audience are called performers including actors comedians dancers musicians and singers
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: performing arts are also supported by workers in related fields such as songwriting and stagecraft
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: performers often adapt their appearance such as with costumes and stage makeup etc.there is also a specialized form of fine art in which the artists perform their work live to an audience
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: this is called performance art
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: most performance art also involves some form of plastic art perhaps in the creation of props
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: dance was often referred to as a plastic art during the modern dance era
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: ;music music as an academic discipline mainly focuses on two career paths music performance focused on the orchestra and the concert hall and music education training music teachers
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: students learn to play instruments but also study music theory musicology history of music and composition
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: in the liberal arts tradition music is also used to broaden skills of non musicians by teaching skills such as concentration and listening
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: ;theater theatre or theater greek theatron oeatpov is the branch of the performing arts concerned with acting out stories in front of an audience using combinations of speech gesture music dance sound and spectacle &mdash indeed any one or more elements of the other performing arts
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: in addition to the standard narrative dialogue style theatre takes such forms as opera ballet mime kabuki classical indian dance chinese opera mummers plays and pantomime
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: dance from old french dancier perhaps from frankish generally refers to human movement either used as a form of expression or presented in a social spiritual or performance setting
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: dance is also used to describe methods of non verbal communication see body language between humans or animals bee dance mating dance motion in inanimate objects the leaves danced in the wind and certain musical forms or genres
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: choreography is the art of making dances and the person who does this is called a choreographer
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: definitions of what constitutes dance are dependent on social cultural aesthetic artistic and moral constraints and range from functional movement such as folk dance to codified virtuoso techniques such as ballet
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri

lines.value: in sports gymnastics figure skating and synchronized swimming are dance disciplines while martial arts kata are often compared to dances
lines.name: Bishnupriya Manipuri
